      <title>惠誉表示，医院未来将面临更多信用评级下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/fitch-sees-more-credit-rating-downgrades-ahead-for-hospitals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于医疗保健实体难以从大流行中恢复过来，非营利医院部门的评级可能会继续下调。]]></description>
